            <title>[THRIFT-1009] TUnion does not correctly deep copy a ByteBuffer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1009</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a TUnion makes a deep copy of an object, it currently returns the original byte buffer when the union is set to be a byte buffer.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should be changed to a TBaseHelper.copyBinary call.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
